title: Qataris to bid for Manchester United
description: Investors linked to the Qatari royal family will bid to buy Manchester United on Friday.

title: Three unidentified objects shot down by US 'most likely' linked to private companies, Biden says
description: Three unidentified objects shot down by the US did not appear to have been used for spying and were likely tied to benign purposes, Joe Biden has said.

title: 362,000 Teslas recalled in US over fears full self-driving software may cause crashes
description: Tesla is recalling hundreds of thousands of cars in the United States over fears their full self-driving (FSD) software may cause a crash.

title: Starmer meets Zelenskyy in first trip to Ukraine as opposition leader
description: Sir Keir Starmer has met with Volodymyr Zelenskyy today as he made his first visit to Ukraine since Russia's invasion last February.

title: Antarctica's 'Doomsday' glacier is 'in trouble'
description: Antarctica's vast Thwaites glacier, which could push up global sea levels by half a metre because of its melting ice, is "in trouble", according to scientists.

title: What is Marburg virus? The Ebola-like disease spreading in parts of Africa
description: A Marburg virus outbreak has been detected in Equatorial Guinea, prompting an urgent meeting by the World Health Organisation (WHO) amid fears it could spread.
